  %article{:class => "personal_website"}
    %header
      %h3 @edmore_moyo
      %a [+]
    %p This site is crafted in Ruby, Rails, JavaScript, jQuery, HTML5, HAML and CSS3. I am using RSpec, Steak and Capybara for testing.
    %p The site is currently optimized for Webkit browsers(Chrome and Safari), Firefox and Opera. No full IE optimization as yet.
    %p
      A special thanks to the guy at
      %a{ :href => "http://www.komodomedia.com", :class => "popup"} Komodo Media
      for the superb social media icons,
      %a{:href => "http://www.disqus.com", :class => "popup"} Disqus
      for their commenting application and
      %a{:href => "http://seaofclouds.com", :class => "popup"} Seaofclouds
      for the twitter plugin.
